Lately hackers have found a brand new way to steal sensitive data and it is all about capturing the flow of photons bounced from surface. It may look like spying through telescope not with your eyes, but with special photo elements.	This is very good method of snooping by the person. One and the most important things that hackers can get around is encryption. Even if victim has a fully encrypted hard disk with all information, the operating system should decrypt it so that the user could work with data. Here comes this method like a brilliant for intercepting all texts and images which is displayed on the screen.
